                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/6386" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-1005</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">9158 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">借我东风起，扶摇上青云——龙源电力吸收合并平庄能源</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Get&#160;the&#160;Firm&#160;Force&#160;of&#160;Wind&#160;to&#160;Hit&#160;the&#160;High&#160;Sky -- the Way for Longyuan Power to Absorb and Merge Pingzhuang Energy</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">邱卫林，冯松松</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">东华理工大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">龙源电力集团股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">能源工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务资产部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">21 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">吸收合并；资产重组；并购</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">absorption merger; asset reorganization; mergers and acquisitions</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本案例是一个描述与分析型案例，基于龙源电力吸收合并平庄能源这一案件展开。龙源电力和平庄能源同属于能源行业的上市公司，在平庄能源濒临退市、龙源电力在港股融资困难以及其他多重背景下，龙源电力通过换股并购的方式吸收合并平庄能源对双方来说都是最佳选择。这项并购涉及换股吸收合并、重大资产重组、股权结构等方面，在为中国其他企业的收购行为提供现实参考的同时，也为企业的发展提供了素材，希望通过本次案例的学习，学习者能够深刻了解并掌握企业并购过程中的重要环节和关键理论。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">This&#160;case&#160;is&#160;a&#160;combination&#160;of&#160;description&#160;and&#160;analysis，and it based on  Longyuan Power absorption and merger of  Pingzhuang Energy launched. Longyuan Power and Pingzhuang Energy are both public companies in the energy industry, under the multiple background that Pingzhuang Energy on the verge of delisting, Longyuan Power in Hong Kong stocks financing difficulties, Longyuan Power absorbed and merged Pingzhuang energy through share exchange absorption merger, which is the best choice for both sides. This M&amp;A involves stock exchange, absorption and merge, major asset restructuring, ownership structure and other aspects.  It not only provides realistic reference for the acquisition behavior of other Chinese companies, but also provides materials for the development of the enterprises. It is  hoped that through the study of this case, learners can deeply understand and master the important links and key theories in the process of corporate mergers and acquisitions.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《财务会计理论与实务》、《收购兼并与重组》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">换股吸收合并的概念、特点；换股吸收合并的比例确定方法；企业并购的协同效应；相关理论与分析方法；企业自身、行业及合并后可能带来的风险；开放式讨论</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022-07</td>
                            </tr>
